But [C]that didn't keep the [G]old man from writing
His [D7]eyes lit up with the [G]stars
He said [C]organ man go [G]write down the music
And we'll [D7]play it on a small soft [G]guitar
Silent night holy night
[D7]All is calm [G]all is [G7]bright
[C]Round yon Virgin [G]Mother and Child
[C]Holy Infant so [G]tender and mild
[D7]Sleep in heavenly [G]peace
Sleep in [D7]heavenly [G]peace

